<main class="container">

  <section>
    <h1>Contact &amp; About</h1>
    <p class="lead">This website supports the Lenches weekly newsletter and gathers village news, events and information in one place.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Get in touch</h2>
    <div class="card">
      <p class="mt0">For anything to do with the newsletter or website — corrections, questions or feedback — email
        <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}">{{ site.email }}</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="submit">
    <h2>Submit something for the newsletter</h2>
    <p>Got an event, notice or bit of news? Send it to <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}">{{ site.email }}</a> by the <strong>end of Wednesday</strong> and we'll aim to include it in Thursday's newsletter and here on the site. A short paragraph and, if you have one, a poster or photo is ideal.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="privacy">
    <h2>Privacy note</h2>
    <p>If you sign up for the newsletter, we use your email address only to send you the weekly newsletter via our email provider. We don't sell or share it, and you can unsubscribe at any time using the link in any newsletter, or by emailing us.</p>
  </section>

</main>
